{"tid":765574,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女人變左心係咪就一定唔會返黎？","createTime":"2018-08-03T01:53:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T03:05:00.000Z","uid":43870,"like":21,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"6cd9bb5b95300078c418de958e547e585467bed8","tid":765574,"uid":43870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T01:53:53.000Z","msg":"一齊左7年幾<br />\n中學開始 捱過左4年long d<br />\n以為返到黎係幸福嘅開始<br />\n但自己因為時間耐左所以一直忽略左佢<br />\n直到佢返左大公司 搵錢多左 接觸嘅野又多左<br />\n導致我地距離越黎越遠<br />\n佢有男同事追佢 我因為自卑覺得配佢唔起 所以我講分手<br />\n分左手呢幾個月我好後悔 一直想同佢一齊返 證明自己可以俾到幸福佢<br />\n死纏爛打 冇哂尊嚴<br />\n可惜做乜都已經冇用<br />\n可能佢念舊情佢冇block我 但已經唔再覆我<br />\n我知佢過得好好 唔再需要我<br />\n我每分每秒仲諗住佢 好想佢返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有時都覺得自己好on9係自己放走人 <br />\n但我知道呢一關我地遲早都要面對<br />\n過到呢一關我地我地就會一生一世<br />\n可惜佢已經走得好遠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7749d71c6fddefdda83ddfe01d1be1f1a407ac6a","tid":765574,"uid":120715,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T01:57:08.000Z","msg":"睇黎你最後用另一種愛祝福佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b8a97718b95ed7d6f4d3172a1a9a34deb8b8ecc","tid":765574,"uid":140798,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T01:59:46.000Z","msg":"收埋你份愛啦<br />\n三五七年有緣可以喺返埋一齊"},{"pid":"054fa26d4cd318336d5ce8429321fe58d436002e","tid":765574,"uid":43870,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7749d71c6fddefdda83ddfe01d1be1f1a407ac6a","tid":765574,"uid":120715,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T01:57:08.000Z","msg":"睇黎你最後用另一種愛祝福佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T02:00:32.000Z","msg":